name: APGovernmentTestPrep
0:
”Alexa, open government prep”
”start a new game”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: government prep
des: This skill is designed to help users prepare for the AP Government exam. It has hundreds questions from test prep books as well as released AP exams. They are broken down into randomized 10 question quizzes. The user will get feedback on what the correct answer is as well as their score at the end of the quiz so they can see how they did and how much they need to improve.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
